uperior</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒咁多位巴打既資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我今晚放工返去間七仔試下<br />\n我自己以後都會睇返清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今晚放工先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，個經理都可能收左工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申做過7仔</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪即係玩完...嘈到佢地Call返經理有無機</blockquote><br />\n你點都有得退，放心<br />\n因為之前有人用過呢招呃客錢<br />\n搞唔掂就報警得嫁啦"},{"pid":"62933fc08efd5d21cf4a744813a4f989abaf12de","tid":36703,"uid":27954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"佢每晚會數錢對數<br />\n如果係咁琴晚部機一定有多錢出黎<br />\n多左咁多幾錢 最大粒個個一定知<br />\n但如果佢死口唔忍你唯有報警搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82832647a5cf70649f742b05c9eced0c5a29690","tid":36703,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T02:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Check到，經理可以睇到八達通紀錄，睇番你張八達通number睇番邊個時段入錢，睇番果陣既閉路就一清二楚<br />\n<br />\n利伸，對手舖既superior</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒咁多位巴打既資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我今晚放工返去間七仔試下<br />\n我自己以後都會睇返清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今晚放工先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，個經理都可能收左工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申做過7仔</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪即係玩完...嘈到佢地Call返經理有無機</blockquote><br />\n你點都有得退，放心<br />\n因為之前有人用過呢招呃客錢<br />\n搞唔掂就報警得嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n咁都好啲，我都諗如果搞唔掂報警算數"},{"pid":"2683ec08352223c085d7527ffdf6094c56a7a1ae","tid":36703,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T02:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢每晚會數錢對數<br />\n如果係咁琴晚部機一定有多錢出黎<br />\n多左咁多幾錢 最大粒個個一定知<br />\n但如果佢死口唔忍你唯有報警搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkg